data.description: Deeded Beach Access!  Recent upgrades to this home have significantly enhanced its overall appeal and value. The entire interior has been freshly painted, and notable improvements include a newly installed chandelier in the piano room, updated medicine cabinets in both the master and second bathrooms, and a new sink in the downstairs bathroom. All failing windows have been replaced and screens added as well as a new heat pump. The exterior has seen a transformation with new lighting, a lamppost, fencing, rain gutters at the rear of the home, and a drip water system. The mother-in-law unit above the garage has also been updated with new hardwood flooring, updated heating, blinds, and a renovated bathroom offering increased comfort and privacy for your visitors. At the heart of this home lies a beautifully updated kitchen, showcasing elegant granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, catering to culinary enthusiasts. For gardening enthusiasts, a spacious garden area has been updated and improved and awaits your green thumb. Additionally, ample space for RV and boat parking caters to adventure seekers, making this residence a true coastal haven.  Experience the epitome of coastal living with this remarkable residence, boasting exclusive deeded access to the ocean beach and Winchuck River just a short stroll away. The location emphasizes the home's charm and desirability. Nestled on a generous .40-acre corner lot, this bright and sunny 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom farmhouse is perfect for various outdoor activities.
